Definition: a set of techniques for exploring underlying motives and a method of treating various mental disorders
Example: based on the theories of Sigmund Freud; his physician recommended psychoanalysis
Synonyms: adj, pert, psychoanalytic, psychoanalytical, analysis, verb, cognition, analyze, depth_psychology, psychotherapy, a, set, of, techniques, for, exploring, underlying, motives, and, method, treating, various, mental, disorders, based, on, the, theories, Sigmund, Freud, his, physician, recommended
Category: noun.act
